<typeStatus id="DC46A0C24C4AFFBDFEE9FC036E08FC45" box="[312,376,993,1017]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Types</typeStatus>
</emphasis>
: The specimen in 
<collectionCode id="65EC86A54C4AFFBDFD9DFC036DD2FC44" box="[588,674,993,1016]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">MSNM</collectionCode>
: 
<collectingCountry id="7BEA5EF04C4AFFBDFD7EFC036C4BFC44" box="[687,827,993,1016]" name="South Africa" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">South Africa</collectingCountry>
(Eastern Cape): 
<number id="B5350C474C4AFFBDFC29FC036B75FC44" box="[1016,1029,993,1016]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" value="1.0">1</number>
ɗ, Willowmore, 
<date id="774338A04C4AFFBDFB6EFC036A5AFC44" box="[1215,1322,993,1016]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" value="1907-01-20">
20.1. 
<number id="B5350C474C4AFFBDFB22FC036A5AFC44" box="[1267,1322,993,1016]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" value="1907.0">1907</number>
</date>
